import { AiOutlineStrikethrough, AiFillMail, AiOutlineLinkedin, AiFillGithub, } from "react-icons/ai"; import React from "react"; import mine from "../assets/img/mine.png"; export default function about() { return (

1. About Me

Hello, I'm ShivRaj Singh, and I enjoy creating things that live on the internet. My primary focus and specialization lie in{" "} React.Js. With a strong background in{" "} Express.js, I am adept at crafting dynamic and interactive web interfaces.

My journey as a developer has allowed me to expand my knowledge and work with a diverse set of technologies. I have hands-on experience with{" "} TypeScript, React, Node, MongoDB, Llm , Api and Express , enabling me to build robust and scalable applications.

My tech stack includes:

React

Tailwind/CSS

Express/Node.js

AWS, Next Js

TensorFlow, Bash, Figma, C/C++

TypeScript, JavaScript(ES6+)

Three.js, Redux

Bootstrap, jQuery

PostMan, Api

Currently, I'm learning:

Solid.js

LLM/ BlockChain

Ai Models (LLama2, Gpt3.5 Turbo)

ShivrajSingh.info.me@gmail.com
); }
